+     * \param[in]    cfg     Configuration buffer to use
+     *
+     * \retval #VPX_CODEC_OK
+     *     The configuration was populated.
+     * \retval #VPX_CODEC_INCAPABLE
+     *     Interface is not an encoder interface.
+     * \retval #VPX_CODEC_INVALID_PARAM
